The published ObjectStorageBucket kind reuses
the Bucket SDK family and resolves namespaceName
from observed status first, then through a
GetNamespace lookup when spec.namespace is
omitted.
Successful create and update responses without
lifecycle fields are treated as synchronous
success and projected directly into status,
including status.status.ocid.
Delete keeps the finalizer until DeleteBucket
succeeds and a follow-up read confirms the
bucket is gone.
